  { id: 101, name: 'Australian Dwarf Goat' },
  { id: 202, name: 'Booted Goat' },
  { id: 303, name: 'Pygmy Goat' }
];
and you want to do any of the following:Insert an item into the collection at any index

Delete an item from the collection

Sort the collection

Shuffle the items in the collection

...etc.

A naÃ¯ve approach to creating fields for each item is by index:// in connected component's render()
